.7D-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 45\">Chapter 45</a>, The Blind Girl.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-14\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-14\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>The Guardian</i>: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/books/2014/aug/11/george-rr-martin-in-quotes-i-love-writing-about-bastards\">George RR Martin in quotes: 'I love writing about bastards'</a>, 12 August 2014</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403121251\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.169 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.404 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 4216/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12517/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 28631/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 5337/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 15462/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.210/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.64 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  370.610      1 -total\n 83.25%  308.525      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 82.91%  307.260      1 Template:Infobox\n 15.93%   59.052     46 Template:Ref\n 11.61%   43.036     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  9.41%   34.867     46 Template:Ref/core\n  4.93%   18.279      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  4.17%   15.460     10 Template:Quote\n  1.60%    5.938      1 Template:References\n  1.34%    4.980      1 Template:Date\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoia